headline: Health Net Providing Special Assistance to Members Affected by the Atmospheric Rivers Due to the "2025 Late December Storms" in Los Angeles, Orange, Riverside, San Bernardino, San Diego, and Shasta Counties
summary: In response to Gov. Gavin Newsom's declared state of emergency in Los Angeles, Orange, Riverside, San Bernardino, San Diego, and Shasta Counties, Health Net, one of California's most experienced Medi-Cal managed care health plans and company of Centene Corporation (NYSE: CNC), is providing special assistance to members affected by the atmospheric rivers due to the 2025 late December storms.
